8":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"基于以上痛点，Hydro 开创性的使用了插件系统，提供了一套完整的开发 API 供开发者使用，开发者基于提供的较稳定的 API 进行功能的编写，而无需过多关心内部实现，将功能拆分成多个最小的单元，允许用户根据需要进行自由组合，并在多个版本间达到一致性，同时提供热重载功能，提升开发效率。"},"469":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step0-为什么使用插件","content":"此教程将以编写剪贴板插件为例进行插件开发的说明。"},"470":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step1-初始化项目","content":"前置条件：NodeJS>=22"},"471":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#step1-初始化项目","content":"使用 hydrooj addon create 快速在 /root/addon 下初始化一个插件或是在一个空文件夹中运行 yarn init 并按照提示填写相关信息。"},"472":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"有时我们希望使用本机的 IDE 编写插件上传到服务器（我们也推荐这么做，编辑器提供的代码补全可以很大程度简化开发流程），可以进行如下操作："},"473":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"在本机安装 NodeJS 和 yarn 。"},"474":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"参照步骤 1 使用 yarn init 创建一个项目。"},"475":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"使用 VSCode 打开插件文件夹。"},"476":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript#可选在本机环境编写插件","content":"使用 yarn add hydrooj -D 安装相关开发组件。"},"477":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/typescript-21","page_id":"