"/docs/Hydro/plugins/fps-importer#从-fps-文件导入题目","content":"zip 文件，其中包含了一个或多个 fps 格式的 xml 文件"},"681":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/fps-importer-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/fps-importer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/fps-importer#从-fps-文件导入题目","content":"由于防止解析 fps 文件消耗大量内存，系统默认拒绝导入超过 64MiB 的文件;\nxml 文件需要为 UTF8 编码，否则可能出现中文题面乱码；\n在新版本 fps-importer 中，管理员可以修改导入文件大小限制，但请注意，我们仍不建议您导入过大的题目包。\n若您的文件超过大小限制，可考虑先在本地使用 Easy-Fps-Viewer 等工具进行拆分。"},"682":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/geoip","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/geoip","type":"page","content":"GeoIP","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/geoip"},"683":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/geoip-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/geoip","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/geoip","content":"插件需要 MaxMind 的 Geolite2-City.mmdb 支持，在安装插件后需要将mmdb拷贝至插件同一目录下方可启用，如果你不知道这是什么，请勿安装。"},"684":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"page","content":"hydrojudge","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge"},"685":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#准备","content":"准备"},"686":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#安装","content":"安装"},"687":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为附加组件","content":"作为附加组件"},"688":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"作为独立进程"},"689":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#更新","content":"更新"},"690":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydroju