judge-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为附加组件","content":"重启 Hydro 后 hydrojudge 即可正常运行。"},"711":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"该方法可以帮助您在任意服务器上部署评测机。"},"712":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"type: warn"},"713":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-28","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"我们推荐所有独立评测机使用相同配置机器并关闭内置评测机, 以保证评测结果的稳定性。系统设置中的评测机相关选项仅控制内置评测机, 独立评测机需要在 judge.yaml 中进行设置。"},"714":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-29","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"首先需要创建一个有 PRIV_JUDGE 权限的账户，具体方法参照 此处。（在部署 Hydro 的服务器上运行）"},"715":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-30","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"然后在运行评测机的服务器上安装 HydroJudge ："},"716":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-31","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"创建目录 ~/.config/hydro，在该目录下创建文件 judge.yaml，配置文件格式如下："},"717":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-32","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#作为独立进程","content":"设置完之后，使用下面的指令即可开始运行（可以使用 pm2 管理）："},"718":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-33","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge#更新","content":"HydroJudge 会发布不定期更新。您可以使用 yarn global upgrade-interactive --latest 来检测并进行更新。"},"719":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/hydrojudge-34","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/pl