e_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-hustoj-升级","content":"dataDir: HUSTOJ 中 data 文件夹的位置（这里存储着题目数据等关键信息，需要手动处理）（OJ_DATA）"},"834":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-23","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-hustoj-升级","content":"uploadDir: HUSTOJ 中 上传文件的位置（这里存储着上传的图片和文件等信息，通常为 /home/judge/src/web/upload/）"},"835":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-24","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-hustoj-升级","content":"当脚本运行完成后，请重启 Hydro 实例，会自动完成之后的升级操作。\n迁移后，请使用原 HUSTOJ 的管理员账号登录实例。"},"836":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"SYZOJ 与 HUSTOJ 迁移方法类似，迁移脚本应运行名为 migrateSyzoj 的脚本外，SYZOJ无需 contestType 参数。\n其参数格式如下："},"837":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"host: 数据库地址"},"838":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"port: 数据库端口"},"839":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-28","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"name: 数据库名，一般为 syzoj"},"840":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-29","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"username&password: 账号密码，若无则填写空字符串"},"841":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-30","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"domainId: 迁入的域，默认为 system"},"842":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-31","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"dataDir: SYZOJ 中 data 文件夹的位置（这里存储着题目数据等关键信息，需要手动处理）"},"843":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-32","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-syzoj-升级","content":"由于SYZOJ脚本会将原站所有数据迁移，所以运行耗时较长。\n当脚本运行完成后，请重启 Hydro 实例，会自动完成之后的升级操作。\n迁移后，请使用原 SYZOJ 的管理员账号登录实例。"},"844":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-33","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-universaloj-升级","content":"UniversalOJ （常称作UOJ社区版）与前两者迁移方法类似，迁移脚本应运行名为 migrateUniversalOJ 的脚本。"},"845":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-34","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-universaloj-升级","content":"由于其升级过程较为麻烦，安装脚本已提供自动升级服务，如您需要可运行安装脚本一键迁移，手动迁移请在开发群中提问。"},"846":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-35","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-universaloj-升级","content":"由于UniversalOJ脚本会将原站所有数据迁移，所以运行耗时较长。\n当脚本运行完成后，请重启 Hydro 实例，会自动完成之后的升级操作。\n迁移后，请使用原 UniversalOJ 的管理员账号登录实例。"},"847":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-36","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"type: warn"},"848":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-37","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"迁移会删除当前 Hydro 的所有数据（含用户账户信息）并移入 vj4 的数据。请注意备份相关文件。"},"849":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-38","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","content":"请先完成 Hydro 的部署并完成对文件服务的配置(setting_file)。在迁移数据之前，请先停止正在运行的 vj4 服务，仅保留其数据库开启。请注意 Hydro 所在的数据库不应和源 vj4 数据库相同。若您使用 vj4-docker ，可更改 docker-compose.yml 将数据库映射至其他本机端口。"},"850":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate-39","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/migrate#从-vijos-升级","con